test_name: Consisitency in family/friend contact across forms
short_desc: If CHILDCOMM  >2  (several times a month or more)  and Form A2 INRELTO=2 (Child) and Form A2 INCNTFRQ = 6 (less than once a month)
full_desc: If Q24. CHILDCOMM (Frequency of communication with children?) >2 (several times month or more) and Form A2 Q1. INRELTO (relationship to participant) = 2 (Child) and Form A2 Q4a1. INCNTFRQ (primary contact freq w/participant) = 6 (less than once a month)

test_name: Consisitency in family/friend contact across forms
short_desc: If CHILDCOMM <=2 and Form A2 INRELTO=2 (Child) and Form A2 INCNTFRQ < 6 (>monthly)
full_desc: If Q24. CHILDCOMM (Frequency of communication with children?) <=2 (several times a year or less) and Form A2 Q1. INRELTO (relationship to participant) = 2 (Child) and Form A2 Q4a1. INCNTFRQ (primary contact freq w/participant) < 6 (more than monthly)

test_name: Consisitency in family/friend contact across forms
short_desc:
If FRIENDCOMM is >2 and Form A2 INRELTO (Friend, neighbor, or someone known through family,
friends, work, or community (e.g., church)) andForm A2 INCNTFRQ is 6 (less than once a month)
full_desc: If Q25. FRIENDCOMM (Frequency of communication with friends?) >2 (several times month or more) and Form A2 Q1. INRELTO (relationship to participant) = 5 (Friend, neighbor, or someone known through family, friends, work, or community (e.g., church)) and Form A2 Q4a1. INCNTFRQ (primary contact freq w/participant) = 6 (less than once a month)

test_name: Consisitency in family/friend contact across forms
short_desc:
If FRIENDCOMM is <=2 and Form A2 INRELTO (Friend, neighbor, or someone known through family,
friends, work, or community (e.g., church)) and Form A2 INCNTFRQ is < 6 (>monthly)
full_desc: If Q25. FRIENDCOMM (Frequency of communication with friends?) <=2 (several times a year or less) and Form A2 Q1. INRELTO (relationship to participant) = 5 (Friend, neighbor, or someone known through family, friends, work, or community (e.g., church)) and Form A2 Q4a1. INCNTFRQ (primary contact freq w/participant) < 6 (more than monthly)

short_desc: If EATLESS = 0 and EATLESSYR should not equal 1
full_desc: If Q11. EATLESS (Ever eaten less due to money?) = 0 (No) then Q12. EATLESSYR (Eaten less this year due to money?) should not equal 1 (Yes)

short_desc: If LESSMEDS = 0 and LESSMEDSYR should not equal 1
full_desc: If Q13. LESSMEDS (Ever taken less prescriptions due to money?) = 0 (No), and Q14. LESSMEDSYR (Taken less presriptions this year due to money?) should not equal 1 (Yes)
